The main fetaures of the Hotle Managment System are listed as below:
1. Room Booking
  View available rooms
  Book room
  Cancel booking
  Update booking
2. Customer Registration
   Add customer details
   Search customer
   Update customer
   Delete customer
3. Billing System
   Room charges
   Food charges
   Service charges
   Automatic bill generation
4. Employee Management
   Add employee
   Remove employee
   Update employee details
5. Admin Control
   View all records
   Delete records
   Generate reports
   File management
6. File Handling
   Save customer records
   Save booking details
   Save employee details
   Read records from files
7. Exception Handling
   Invalid room number
   Invalid customer input
   Invalid billing values
